  "detailed_description": "<h1>Join the Community</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Greetings, Settlers!</h2>Welcome to the Alpha Centauri Settlement.<br>Settler, this is your home. Located near the marshlands of this alien planet, it's the perfect place to rest your worn-out body. I hope you like it. <br><br>This place is your digital refuge. Visit whenever things aren't going well. Your stay will help you tackle real-life tasks while keeping you calm and relaxed, by providing built-in productivity features and a soothing environment.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2965050/extras/63827f5c19026ed529b113cf5eab9c82.poster.avif?t=1726428005\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2965050/extras/63827f5c19026ed529b113cf5eab9c82.webm?t=1726428005\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2965050/extras/63827f5c19026ed529b113cf5eab9c82.mp4?t=1726428005\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Keep this digital comfort zone on the side of your screen while burning the midnight oil. With its low memory usage and 'Always on Top' feature, you can run it alongside other applications.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2965050/extras/315c863ad8e0b91858ce52720a5214ed.poster.avif?t=1726428005\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2965050/extras/315c863ad8e0b91858ce52720a5214ed.webm?t=1726428005\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2965050/extras/315c863ad8e0b91858ce52720a5214ed.mp4?t=1726428005\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2>This is a hybrid of a productivity tool and game. Use provided productivity features and unlock new customization items as reward.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Productivity Tools</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2965050/extras/df0686a9598ca6d1b392aba25b0d5551.poster.avif?t=1726428005\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2965050/extras/df0686a9598ca6d1b392aba25b0d5551.webm?t=1726428005\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2965050/extras/df0686a9598ca6d1b392aba25b0d5551.mp4?t=1726428005\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Timers</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>A Pomodoro timer and a classic alarm is provided. </li></ul></li><li><strong>To-do List</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Track and complete your real-life task one by one</li></ul></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Customization</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2965050/extras/0dfe74acb1628c48af4d2711940d1441.poster.avif?t=1726428005\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2965050/extras/0dfe74acb1628c48af4d2711940d1441.webm?t=1726428005\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2965050/extras/0dfe74acb1628c48af4d2711940d1441.mp4?t=1726428005\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Customize Your Alien Second Body</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Choose your current mood, and your alien body will reflect it. <br></li><li>Unlock new customization items to make your alien even more stylish</li></ul></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Cozy and Comforting Environment</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2965050/extras/4ef45d8aa9b4018389df1d3e30e98193.poster.avif?t=1726428005\" width=594 height=334 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2965050/extras/4ef45d8aa9b4018389df1d3e30e98193.webm?t=1726428005\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2965050/extras/4ef45d8aa9b4018389df1d3e30e98193.mp4?t=1726428005\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Choose Your Own Focus Music</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Curated playlists are included<br></li><li>Import your own music and create custom playlist </li></ul></li><li><strong>Delicate and Versatile Lighting</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> The light from the window will reflect your local time and change smoothly as time passes.<br></li><li> Light intensity will adjust based on your settings, including curtain closure or indoor lighting preferences.</li></ul></li><li><strong>Friendly Visitors</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Alpha Centauri is home to cat-like native species, Nyan. They will visit your home from time to time. Greet them and fill your Nyan dictionary. </li></ul></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >And More</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Built-in \"Always on Top\" setting<br></li><li>Low memory usage; runs well with other applications</li></ul>",
